sourcesContent: import styled, { css } from "styled-components"; const Noticias = styled.div` display: flex; justify-content: space-around; align-items: center; margin-top: 4rem; @media (max-width: 675px) { overflow-x: scroll; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; width: 100%; margin-right: -1rem; margin-left: 1rem; scroll-snap-type: x mandatory; justify-content: flex-start; padding: 2rem; img { min-width: 25rem; } } `; const ContainerImgNoticia = styled.div``; const ImgNoticia = styled.img``; const ListaNoticias = () => ( ); export default ListaNoticias;
